  "code": "stateDiagram-v2\n    [IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic] --> New : Process created\n    New --> Ready : Admit (IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController)\n    Ready --> Running : Dispatch (IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode)\n    Running --> Waiting : I/O or event wait\n    Running --> Ready : Interrupt (IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode)\n    Running --> Terminated : Exit (IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream)\n    \n    Waiting --> Ready : I/O completed\n    Waiting --> Suspended_Wait : Swap out (IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic)\n    Suspended_Wait --> Suspended_Ready : I/O completed\n    Suspended_Ready --> Ready : Swap in (IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker)\n    \n    Terminated --> [IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic]",
