    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为工业物联网场景设计一个进程状态图，核心是PLC逻辑控制器作为整个生命周期的起点和终点。系统里还有边缘节点、执行器控制器、MQTT代理和遥测数据流这些关键组件。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode",
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController",
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker",
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，PLC逻辑作为容器节点。那进程创建之后首先进入什么状态？是直接可运行还是需要先经过某个中间状态？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "New",
        "Process created"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "进程创建后先进入New状态，然后需要执行器控制器执行Admit操作才能进入Ready状态。这个Admit相当于准入控制，检查资源配额。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "New",
        "Ready",
        "Admit",
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把PLC到New的创建关系，以及New经Admit到Ready的流转画出来。接下来从Ready到Running的触发条件是什么？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "[IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic]",
        "New",
        "Ready",
        "Admit",
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Ready到Running由边缘节点执行Dispatch操作，这是任务调度。另外Running状态要有三条出路：I/O等待进入Waiting、被中断回到Ready、或者正常结束到Terminated。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Ready",
        "Running",
        "Dispatch",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode",
        "Waiting",
        "Interrupt",
        "Terminated",
        "Exit"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认一下，Running到Ready的Interrupt也是由边缘节点触发吗？还有Terminated的退出操作由谁执行？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Running",
        "Ready",
        "Interrupt",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode",
        "Terminated",
        "Exit"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Interrupt也是边缘节点。Exit由遥测数据流执行，进程结束后要把数据上报。Terminated最后要回到PLC逻辑，表示资源回收。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Interrupt",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode",
        "Exit",
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream",
        "Terminated",
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加Running的三条分支和Terminated的闭环。Waiting状态的处理逻辑呢？I/O完成后直接回Ready吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Running",
        "Waiting",
        "I/O or event wait",
        "I/O completed",
        "Ready"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "I/O完成确实回Ready，但工业场景有内存压力，需要支持换出。Waiting可以被PLC逻辑Swap out到Suspended_Wait，这是挂起等待状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Waiting",
        "Ready",
        "I/O completed",
        "Suspended_Wait",
        "Swap out",
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "Suspended_Wait之后呢？如果I/O完成了但进程还在挂起状态，怎么流转？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Suspended_Wait",
        "I/O completed"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Suspended_Wait在I/O完成后变成Suspended_Ready，表示资源就绪但还在外存。然后需要MQTT代理执行Swap in换入，才能回到Ready状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Suspended_Wait",
        "Suspended_Ready",
        "I/O completed",
        "Swap in",
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker",
        "Ready"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，挂起链路也补全了。我检查一下：PLC创建进程，经Admit、Dispatch进入运行，运行时可中断回就绪、等待I/O、或退出上报，等待时可换出，挂起链路由MQTT代理换入。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "[IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic]",
        "New",
        "Ready",
        "Running",
        "Waiting",
        "Suspended_Wait",
        "Suspended_Ready",
        "Terminated"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "流程是对的，但确认一下各个触发组件的标注都正确：Admit是执行器控制器，Dispatch和Interrupt都是边缘节点，Exit是遥测流，Swap out是PLC逻辑，Swap in是MQTT代理。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Admit",
